room_title: Escape room "Roaring Dan's Pirate Dungeon" by Escape Artistry in Chicago
review: We had a great experience at the EScape Artistry. Did the Pirates room, challenging, but the agent that was assigned to us was motivating and helpful. With that said we we escaped with two mins to spare! When you book, double check the address. They have more then one location on Milwaukee Ave. Can't wait to do it again!

room_title: Escape room "Roaring Dan's Pirate Dungeon" by Escape Artistry in Chicago
review: Roaring Dan's Pirate Dungeon was among the best escape games I've done in Chicago! I can't wait to return to the Time Gallery and play the rest!

room_title: Escape room "Roaring Dan's Pirate Dungeon" by Escape Artistry in Chicago
review: A great experience! Balanced puzzles with just the right about of guidance and clues, very satisfying results, fun themes, and immersive environments add up to an hour well-spent!
